# CardButton (Momentum) — Momentum guidance (IDE)

**CardButton** **looks** like a **Card** but behaves as a **single button**—**click/keyboard anywhere** on the card (except avoid nested focusables; slots should be **non-interactive** content). Use **`name`** and **`value`** in forms.

See also: [Card](./card.mdc), [CardCheckbox](./cardcheckbox.mdc), [CardRadio](./cardradio.mdc).

Browse the [Momentum Components catalog](https://momentum.design/en/components/) for naming; Storybook documents props and examples. Reference: [Storybook — CardButton / Docs](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/docs/components-card-cardbutton--docs). Optional: [Example](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/story/components-card-cardbutton--example).

---

## Import

Requires <ThemeProvider> and <IconProvider> ancestors. See setup.mdc.

```jsx
import { CardButton, Text } from "@momentum-design/components/dist/react";
```

---

## What it is

- Inherits **card** layout/appearance (`image`, **`before-body`** / **`body`** / **`after-body`**, **`title`**, **`subtitle`**, footer slots). **`icon-button`** header actions may differ from **Card**—confirm slots in Storybook for your version.  
- Fires **`onClick`**, **`onKeyDown`**, **`onKeyUp`**, **`onFocus`**.  
- **Do not** place **`Button`**, **links**, or other nested interactives in slots—**nested interactive** content breaks accessibility. Use plain **`Text`**, static imagery, or decorative icons only.  
- Form props: **`type`**, **`name`**, **`value`** when needed (align with **Buttonsimple** patterns).

**Pick `Card` + footer `Button`** if the design needs **several** actions; pick **`CardButton`** for **one** primary action on the **whole** tile.

---

## Key props

- Same **card** surface props as **Card** (`cardTitle`, `variant`, `orientation`, `imageSrc`, …) plus **`type`**, optionally **`name`**, **`value`**, **`disabled`**, **`softDisabled`**

---

## Example

```jsx
import { CardButton, Text } from "@momentum-design/components/dist/react";


<CardButton
  type="button"
  variant="border"
  orientation="vertical"
  cardTitle="Title"
  subtitle="Subtitle"
  imageSrc="https://picsum.photos/seed/momentum-cardbtn/640/360"
  imageAlt="Decorative card image"
  iconName="placeholder-bold"
  titleTagName="span"
  subtitleTagName="span"
>
  <Text slot="body" tagname="span">
    Body content only—no nested buttons or links inside the card surface.
  </Text>
</CardButton>
```

---

## Checklist for IDE prototypes

- [ ] **`ThemeProvider`** + **`IconProvider`** when using **`iconName`**  
- [ ] **One** action per card surface; no nested **`Button`** / **`Link`** in slots  
- [ ] **`type="button"`** when not submitting a form row  
- [ ] Accessible name from **title** / body text; add **`aria-label`** pattern from Storybook if your version documents it for **`CardButton`**  

Cross-check [Storybook — CardButton / Docs](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/docs/components-card-cardbutton--docs) and your installed package version.
